OL,3,CWhat is a puppy raiser and how do I
OL,4,Cbecome one?
OL,6,FA campaign has been launched to
OL,7,Fencourage people to volunteer to
OL,8,Fbecome puppy raisers, as blind and
OL,9,Fpartially sighted people face waits of
OL,10,Fup to 18 months to be matched with a
OL,11,Fservice dog.
OL,13,FAround 900 visually impaired people
OL,14,Fare currently on the waiting list for
OL,15,Fa guide dog across the UK.
OL,17,FOne of the reasons behind the wait is
OL,18,Fa shortage of volunteers willing to
OL,19,Fraise puppies and help them socialise,
OL,20,Fready for formal training.
