OL,3,CWhat is a puppy raiser and how do I
OL,4,Cbecome one?
OL,6,F"Whereas if you've got a dog, people
OL,7,Fare like, 'ooh, that's a nice dog!'"
OL,9,FLydia has also found that for her a
OL,10,Fguide dog is less taxing than using a
OL,11,Fwhite cane.
OL,13,F"It's being able to do things so much
OL,14,Fmore easily than with a white cane.
OL,15,FLots of people do choose a white
OL,16,Fcanes, but for me a white cane is so
OL,17,Ftactile you end up hitting everything
OL,18,Fbefore you realise you've got there to
OL,19,Fit.
