OL,3,CWhat is a puppy raiser and how do I
OL,4,Cbecome one?
OL,6,F"A dog avoids it, and you don't know
OL,7,Fit was there in the first place.
OL,9,F"It really reduces the mental load of
OL,10,Fhaving to work out where you are all
OL,11,Fthe time."
OL,13,FLiz Graham is one of the volunteer
OL,14,Fpuppy raisers Guide Dogs UK needs more
OL,15,Fof. She finds the puppy-raising
OL,16,Fexperience to be hugely rewarding.
OL,18,FLiz said: "I've always kept in mind
OL,19,Fthat you're not raising a pet as such,
OL,20,Fyou're raising somebody's independence.
