OL,3,CWhat is a puppy raiser and how do I
OL,4,Cbecome one?
OL,6,F"I've absolutely loved every minute of
OL,7,Fit. It's obviously difficult - anyone
OL,8,Fwho's had a puppy knows there's highs
OL,9,Fand lows - but the highs have
OL,10,Fcertainly exceeded all the lows."
OL,12,FGuide Dogs UK wants to make it clear
OL,13,Fthat those volunteering to raise a
OL,14,Fpuppy will be supported with advice,
OL,15,Falongside free health care and help
OL,16,Fwith food bills.
OL,18,FRachel Adams from the charity said:
OL,19,F"You get regular visits, puppy
OL,20,Fclasses, we do one-to-one home visits,
OL,21,Ftown walks, group sessions.
