OL,3,CWhat is a puppy raiser and how do I
OL,4,Cbecome one?
OL,6,F"There's lots of variety, alongside
OL,7,Four online learning platform, so you
OL,8,Fhave access to things 24/7."
OL,10,FThe hope is that if more volunteers
OL,11,Fhelp to raise puppies, visually
OL,12,Fimpaired people will be paired with a
OL,13,Fcanine companion a lot quicker.
